class phenomedb.models.SavedQuery(**kwargs)

SavedQuery object

Parameters:

  • id (int) – Primary Key

  • name (str) – The name of the SavedQuery

  • description (str) – The description of the SavedQuery

  • json (dict) – The definition of the SavedQuery in JSON format

  • project_short_label (str) – A short label that will be displayed in downstream analyses

  • code_string (str) – The SQLAlchemy representation of the query

  • created_by (str) – The user who created the query

  • date_added (datetime.datetime) – The data the query was added

  • type (phenomedb.models.SavedQuery.Type) – The Type, whether ‘custom’ or ‘preset’, only used by the UI

  • cache_state (dict) – The current cache state of the query result dataframes
